data.description: Located in the best building on Cortez Hill, this bright and airy 2 bedroom unit is an absolute gem. West facing so the condo is flooded with natural light during the day and jaw dropping sunsets behind the iconic El Cortez building in the evenings. Best of both worlds. The unit it self has been upgraded throughout with the following; built-in cabinets, extra lighting, cork (wood) flooring. "EcoBee" thermostat that is app operated, recently replaced shower cartridges, purified water in the kitchen. Aria is a first class building that features a pool, jacuzzi, gym, resident's lounge, community bike storage and full time building staff that includes evening security. Location is A+ with Little Italy, Gaslamp Quarter and the Embarcadero all within waking distance so you can enjoy all the cafes, restaurants, bars and farmer's markets Downtown San Diego has to offer.
